## â“ Frequently Asked Questions

### How do I delete my account?
1. Open the app
2. Go to Settings
3. Select "Delete Account"
4. Confirm deletion

All your data will be permanently removed from our servers.

### How do I reset my affirmations?
Go to your affirmations list and swipe left to delete individual affirmations, or delete your account and start fresh.

### Where is my data stored?
Your affirmations and profile data are securely stored on Supabase servers using encrypted connections. Local data is stored on your device.

### Can I download my data?
Contact us at siegristgianin@gmail.com to request a copy of your data.

### Why isn't my widget updating?
Make sure the app has permission to access your device. Try force-closing and reopening both the app and widget settings.

### How do I enable notifications?
Go to Settings > Notifications and toggle "Daily Reminders" on. You can customize the time and frequency.

### Is my data private?
Yes. We do not share, sell, or track your personal data. See our [Privacy Policy](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Stiler45/s100_legal/main/it_girl_privacy_policy.md) for details.

### Can I use the app offline?
Yes. Your affirmations are stored locally on your device and will be available offline. Syncing and new affirmation generation require internet connection.

